  <brief_title>Inappropriate Medications Associated With Anticholinesterase and/or Memantine Treatment in the Elderly</brief_title>
  <acronym>MIDA</acronym>
  <official_title>Inappropriate Medications and Alzheimer Disease: Prevalence and Associated Factors in Elderly Patients Treated With Anticholinesterase and/or Memantine. MIDA Study.</official_title>
